"otherterm=\"gloss-gnome\">GNOME</glossseealso> <glossseealso otherterm="
"\"gloss-kde\">&kde;</glossseealso> <glossseealso otherterm=\"gloss-qt\">&Qt;"
"</glossseealso>"
